<div3 type="orders" n="1" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head type="nobreak">Attention, Marylanders!</head> 
<p rend="nobreak">

<milestone unit="sentence" n="471" /> --The undersigned, having secured a fine lot of horses, is now raising a <orgName n="Cavalry company" type="company">Cavalry company</orgName>, to be attached to the <orgName type="regiment" key="1VACav">1st Virginia Cavalry</orgName>, under <persName n="Lee,Colonel,Fitz-Hugh,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00291" reg="default:Lee,Fitz-Hugh,,," authname="lee,fitz-hugh"><roleName n="Colonel" full="yes">Col.</roleName> <foreName full="yes">Fitz-Hugh</foreName> <surname full="yes">Lee</surname></persName>, and in connection with <persName n="Gaither,Captain,G.,R.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00292" reg="default:Gaither,G.,R.,," authname="gaither,g.,r."><roleName n="Captain" full="yes">Capt.</roleName> <foreName full="yes">G.</foreName> <foreName full="yes">R.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Gaither</surname></persName>, a Maryland company which has now served with distinction in that regiment for <measure n="14months" type="date">14 months</measure>. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="472" /> Persons disposed to join a company with the certainty of being ready for the field within <num value="1">one</num> week or <measure n="10days" type="date">ten days</measure>, will call at once at <address><street n="Pearl Street 15">No. 15 Pearl street</street></address> and enroll their names.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="473" />Improved army revolvers, just brought over from <placeName reg="Maryland" key="tgn,7007516" authname="tgn,7007516">Maryland</placeName>, will be furnished each man. </p> <closer> <signed><persName n="Smith,,R.,Carter,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00293" reg="default:Smith,R.,Carter,," authname="smith,r.,carter"><foreName full="yes">R.</foreName> <foreName full="yes">Carter</foreName>  <surname full="yes">Smith</surname></persName>,</signed> <rs type="role2">Captain</rs>, <lb /> jy <num value="22">22</num>--4t* Late <orgName type="regiment" key="1MDRegiment">1st Maryland Reg't.</orgName> </closer> </div3> </div2> 
