<div2 type="runaways" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head>Runaways.</head> 
<div3 type="article" n="1" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head type="nobreak"><measure n="150dollars" type="currency">One hundred and fifty dollars</measure> reward.</head> 
<p rend="nobreak">

<milestone unit="sentence" n="481" /> --Ranaway from me on <dateStruct full="yes"><day type="name" full="yes">Sunday</day></dateStruct>, <date value="07-20" authname="--07-20">July 20th,</date> <num value="3">three</num> Negro Boys, namely: </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="482" /> <persName n="Carpenter,,James,A.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00294" reg="default:Carpenter,James,A.,," authname="carpenter,james,a."><foreName full="yes">James</foreName> <foreName full="yes">A.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Carpenter</surname></persName>, brown skin, about <measure n="24years" type="date">24 years</measure> old, <measure n="5feet" type="distance">5 feet</measure> <num value="7">7</num> or <measure n="8inches" type="distance">8 inches</measure> high, reads and writes an indifferent hand.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="483" />He was bought of <persName n="Claybrook,Mister,R.,A.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00295" reg="default:Claybrook,R.,A.,," authname="claybrook,r.,a."><roleName n="Mister" full="yes">Mr.</roleName> <foreName full="yes">R.</foreName> <foreName full="yes">A.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Claybrook</surname></persName>, of <placeName reg="Westmoreland, Pennsylvania" key="tgn,1003017" authname="tgn,1003017">Westmoreland county</placeName>. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="484" /> <persName n="Arthur,,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00296" reg="mostcommon:Arthur,nomatch:0" authname="arthur"><surname full="yes">Arthur</surname></persName>, also brown skin; has been in the employ of <persName n="Cottrell,Mister,S.,S.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00297" reg="default:Cottrell,S.,S.,," authname="cottrell,s.,s."><roleName n="Mister" full="yes">Mr.</roleName> <foreName full="yes">S.</foreName> <foreName full="yes">S.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Cottrell</surname></persName> for some months, about <measure n="5feet" type="distance">5 feet</measure> <num value="6">6</num> or <measure n="7inches" type="distance">7 inches</measure> high; was purchased of <persName n="Bowen,Mister,William,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00298" reg="default:Bowen,William,,," authname="bowen,william"><roleName n="Mister" full="yes">Mr.</roleName> <foreName n="William" full="yes">Wm.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Bowen</surname></persName>, of <placeName reg="Fauquier, Virginia, United States" key="tgn,1002368" authname="tgn,1002368">Fauquier county, Va.</placeName> </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="485" /> <persName n="Scott,,Ned,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00299" reg="default:Scott,Ned,,," authname="scott,ned"><foreName full="yes">Ned</foreName> <surname full="yes">Scott</surname></persName>, of lighter complexion than the rest; about <measure n="5feet" type="distance">5 feet</measure> <measure n="4inches" type="distance">4 inches</measure> high.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="486" />He was purchased of <persName n="Royster,Mister,G.,W.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00300" reg="default:Royster,G.,W.,," authname="royster,g.,w."><roleName n="Mister" full="yes">Mr.</roleName> <foreName full="yes">G.</foreName> <foreName full="yes">W.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Royster</surname></persName>. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="487" /> It is supposed they are trying to make their way to <placeName reg="Fredericksburg, Fredericksburg, Virginia" key="tgn,7013943" authname="tgn,7013943">Fredericksburg</placeName>.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="488" />I will pay the above reward of <measure n="150dollars" type="currency">$150</measure> for all <num value="3">three</num>, or <measure n="50dollars" type="currency">$50</measure> for each <num value="1">one</num>, delivered to me or secured in some jail so that I can get them. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="489" /> jy <num value="22">22</num>--6t* <persName n="Frase,,John,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00301" reg="default:Frase,John,,," authname="frase,john"><foreName full="yes">John</foreName> <surname full="yes">Frase</surname></persName> </p> </div3> 
<div3 type="article" n="2" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head /> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="490" /> A Runaway Negro man, named <persName><foreName full="yes">George</foreName></persName>, the property of <persName n="Webber,Colonel,William,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00302" reg="default:Webber,William,,," authname="webber,william"><roleName n="Colonel" full="yes">Col.</roleName> <foreName n="William" full="yes">Wm.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Webber</surname></persName>, of <placeName reg="Spotsylvania, Spotsylvania, Virginia" key="tgn,2114316" authname="tgn,2114316">Spotsylvania</placeName>, was brought to my jail <date value="1862-07-21" authname="1862-07-21">July 21st, 1862.</date>--Said <persName><foreName full="yes">George</foreName></persName> is of a dark complexion, about <measure n="5feet" type="distance">5 feet</measure> <measure n="8inches" type="distance">8 inches</measure> in height.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="491" />The owner will come forward, pay expenses, and take him away. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="492" /> jy <num value="22">22</num>--7t* <persName n="Lumpkin,,Robert,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00303" reg="default:Lumpkin,Robert,,," authname="lumpkin,robert"><foreName full="yes">Robert</foreName> <surname full="yes">Lumpkin</surname></persName>. </p> </div3> 
<div3 type="article" n="3" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head type="nobreak"><measure n="50dollars" type="currency">Fifty dollars</measure> reward</head> 
<p rend="nobreak">

<milestone unit="sentence" n="493" /> --For the man harboring my boy, <hi rend="smallcaps"><persName n="Lewis,,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00304" reg="mostcommon:Lewis,nomatch:0" authname="lewis"><surname full="yes">Lewis</surname></persName>,</hi> and <measure n="25dollars" type="currency">$25</measure> for the apprehension of the boy, delivered to <hi rend="smallcaps"><persName n="Davis,Mister,Hector,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00305" reg="default:Davis,Hector,,," authname="davis,hector"><roleName n="Mister" full="yes">Mr.</roleName> <foreName full="yes">Hector</foreName> <surname full="yes">Davis</surname></persName>'s</hi> jail, so that I can get him. He was taken about <measure n="6weeks" type="date">six weeks</measure> ago, and seen in <placeName reg="Richmond, Richmond, Virginia" key="tgn,7013964" authname="tgn,7013964">Richmond</placeName> a few days ago, on a horse supposed to be an officer's, and is no doubt in some of the camps.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="494" />The boy is about <measure n="18years" type="date">eighteen years</measure> old, with regular features, dark brown complexion, and about <measure n="5feet" type="distance">five feet</measure> <num value="5">five</num> of <measure n="6inches" type="distance">six inches</measure> high, and has a good countenance. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="495" /> jy <num value="22">22</num>--3t* <persName n="Turner,,C.,B.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00306" reg="default:Turner,C.,B.,," authname="turner,c.,b."><foreName full="yes">C.</foreName> <foreName full="yes">B.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Turner</surname></persName>. </p> </div3> 
<div3 type="article" n="4" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head type="nobreak"><measure n="10dollars" type="currency">Ten dollars</measure> reward.</head> 
<p rend="nobreak">

<milestone unit="sentence" n="496" /> --Ran off from my premises, on Federal street, on <dateStruct value="--16" full="yes" authname="---16"><day reg="16" full="yes">16th inst.</day></dateStruct>, my woman <persName><foreName full="yes">Emily</foreName></persName>.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="497" />She is a bright mulatto, about <measure n="18years" type="date">18 years</measure> of age. She is thought to be making her way for <placeName reg="New Kent, Virginia, United States" key="tgn,1002713" authname="tgn,1002713">New Kent county</placeName>.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="498" />If not, she may be lurking about this city.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="499" />I will give the above reward for her confinement in some jail, so I can get her again.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="500" /><num value="1">One</num> of her eyes was swollen when she left, from cold. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="501" /> jy <num value="19">19</num>--3t* <persName n="Daley,,John,M.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00307" reg="default:Daley,John,M.,," authname="daley,john,m."><foreName full="yes">John</foreName> <foreName full="yes">M.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Daley</surname></persName>. </p> </div3> 
<div3 type="article" n="5" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head type="nobreak">Ran away--<measure n="50dollars" type="currency">$50</measure> reward</head> 
<p rend="nobreak">

<milestone unit="sentence" n="502" /> --From <placeName reg="Howardsville, Albemarle, Virginia" key="tgn,2112332" authname="tgn,2112332">Howardsville, Albemarle county</placeName>, Va, a Negro man, about <measure n="25years" type="date">25 years</measure> old, black, and heavy set, named <hi rend="smallcaps"><persName><foreName full="yes">Tom</foreName></persName>.</hi> The above negro was purchased about <measure n="10days" type="date">ten days</measure> ago, in <placeName reg="Richmond, Richmond, Virginia" key="tgn,7013964" authname="tgn,7013964">Richmond</placeName>, of <persName n="Martin,,J.,H.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00308" reg="default:Martin,J.,H.,," authname="martin,j.,h."><foreName full="yes">J.</foreName> <foreName full="yes">H.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Martin</surname></persName>.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="503" />The negro is from <placeName reg="caroline county, Virginia" key="tgn,1002235" authname="tgn,1002235">Caroline county</placeName>, and may be making his way back.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="504" />The above reward will be paid if delivered to me, or lodged in any jail so that I can get him. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="505" /> jy <num value="16">16</num>--5t* <persName n="Davis,,John,R.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00309" reg="expanded:Davis," authname="davis"><foreName full="yes">John</foreName> <foreName full="yes">R.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Davis</surname></persName>, <placeName reg="Richmond, Richmond, Virginia" key="tgn,7013964" authname="tgn,7013964">Richmond, Va.</placeName> </p> </div3> </div2> 
